Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 sun kalli sauraron da Brett Kavanaugh ya yi
Fiye da mutane miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shaidun kotu a gidan talabijin na kasa da ke birnin New York a ranar Alhamis, inda aka nuna wanda aka nada a matsayin wanda zai zama mai shari'a a kotun kolin kasar, wato Brett Kavanaugh, da kuma Christine Blasey Ford, wadda ta zargi shi da aikata fyade a shekarun 1980.
A wani lokaci kuma, 'yan jarida sun ci gaba da yin tawaye da tashoshin rediyo da ke yaɗa labarai a kan wani abu da ya faru a ranar Jumma'a, wato yarjejeniyar da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya ƙulla, wadda ta ba FBI damar yin bincike na tsawon mako guda a kan zargin da ake yi wa 'yan jarida.
A wani jawabi da Ford ta yi wa kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa, ta ce ta tabbata da cewa Kavanaugh, a cikin maye, ya yi wa matarsa dukan tsiya, ya yi ƙoƙarin cire mata tufafinta a wani bikin da aka yi a makarantar sakandare.
Kavanaugh ya ce a cikin wata shaidar da ya yi, ya tabbatar da cewa bai taba yin hakan ba.
A cewar Nielsen, mai yiwuwa mutane miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli shirin a ranar Juma'a.
Kamfanin ya rubuta matsakaicin masu kallo a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel da MSNBC.
Babu wani adadin da aka samu daga wasu gidajen rediyo da suka nuna shi, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network.
Kuma Nielsen yawanci yana da matsala wajen auna yawan masu kallon shirye-shirye a ofis.
Don a iya kwatanta wannan, wannan adadin masu kallo ne da suka kai adadin masu kallon wasannin NFL ko kuma Oscar.
Fox News Channel, wanda masu watsa shirye-shiryensa suka goyi bayan nadin Kavanaugh, ya yi fice a jerin tashoshin talabijin, inda ya samu ra'ayoyi miliyan 5.69 a lokacin da ake sauraron karar, a cewar Nielsen.
ABC na biyu da masu kallo miliyan 3.26.
Gidan talabijin na CBS yana da miliyan 3.1, NBC na da miliyan 2.94, MSNBC na da miliyan 2.89, kuma CNN na da miliyan 2.52, a cewar Nielsen.
Mutane sun ci gaba da sauraron karar bayan an yi shari'ar.
Flake ne babban jigon wasan kwaikwayon na ranar Juma'a.
Bayan da ofishin 'yan jam'iyyar Republican ya fitar da sanarwar cewa zai zabi Kavanaugh, an kama shi a gaban kyamarorin CNN da CBS a safiyar Juma'a yayin da masu zanga-zanga ke ihu a gare shi yayin da yake kokarin hawa wani lif zuwa gaban kwamitin yanke hukunci.
Ya tsaya a kan fuskarsa har tsawon 'yan mintoci, ana yi masa ba'a, kuma CNN tana watsa shirye-shiryensa kai tsaye.
"Ina tsaye a gabanka", wata mata ta ce.
"Shin, kun yi zaton ya gaya gaskiya ga ƙasar?
An gaya masa, "Kana da iko sosai, kuma mata da yawa ba su da iko".
Flake ya ce ofishinsa ya ba da sanarwa kuma ya ce kafin a rufe lif ɗin cewa yana son ya ƙara magana a lokacin da ake sauraron karar.
Dukan gidajen talabijin na ƙasar sun nuna a kai a kai sa'o'i bayan haka, lokacin da kwamitin da ke yanke hukunci a kan waɗanda suka yi ba'a za su yanke shawara a kan ko a ba Kavanaugh takardar da za ta sa dukan majalisar dattawa ta yi na'am da shi.
Amma Flake ya ce zai yi hakan ne kawai idan ya san cewa hukumar FBI za ta bincika tuhumar da ake yi wa mutumin a mako mai zuwa, kamar yadda 'yan Democrat da ke da rinjaye a majalisar dattawa suka ce su yi.
Flake ya yarda da hakan ne bayan tattaunawar da ya yi da abokinsa Sanata Chris Coons na Democrat.
Bayan ya tattauna da Coons da kuma wasu sanatoci da yawa, Flake ya yanke shawara.
Flake ya yi tasiri a zabensa, saboda a fili yake cewa 'yan Republican ba za su sami kuri'u da za su amince da Kavanaugh ba tare da binciken ba.
Shugaba Trump ya kaddamar da binciken FBI kan zargin da ake wa Kavanaugh.
Firaministan Birtaniya ya zargi masu sukar Brexit da "yin siyasa"
Firayim Minista Theresa May ta zargi masu sukar shirinta na ficewa daga Tarayyar Turai da "yin wasa da siyasar" tare da makomar Birtaniya da kuma lalata bukatun kasa, a wata hira da jaridar Sunday Times.
Firaministan Burtaniya Theresa May ta isa taron jam'iyyar Conservative a Birmingham, Burtaniya, a ranar 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
A wata hira da aka yi da Theresa May a shafin jaridar, tsohon ministan harkokin wajenta Boris Johnson ya kai hari kan shirin Chequers na Brexit, inda ya ce shawarar da aka bayar na Birtaniya da EU su tara wa juna harajin da ake bi "abin dariya ne".
'Yan sanda sun kama Dyteon Simpson, wanda ake zargi da laifin kisan dan wasan LSU'
'Yan sanda sun kama wani da ake zargi da laifin kisan Wayde Sims, dan wasan kwando na 'yan shekaru 20 a LSU.
An kama Dyteon Simpson, ɗan shekara 20, aka tsare shi a kurkuku bisa zargin laifin kisan kai, in ji 'yan sanda a Baton Rouge.
Jami'ai sun saki bidiyon rikicin da ya faru tsakanin Sims da Simpson, kuma 'yan sanda sun ce Sims ya rasa tabarau a lokacin da ake fafatawa.
'Yan sanda sun gano waɗannan tabarau a wurin da aka yi wa Simpson kisan gilla, kuma sun ce sun sami DNA na Simpson a jikinsa, in ji wani rahoto daga WAFB, wani reshen kamfanin CBS.
Bayan sun yi wa Simpson tambayoyi, 'yan sanda sun ce ya yi ikirarin kashe Wayde.
An bayar da belinsa a kan dala 350,000, in ji lauyan.
Likita da ke kula da al'amuran 'yan sanda a yankin Easton Rouge ya ba da rahoton farko a ranar Juma'a, inda ya ce an kashe shi ne da bindiga a kai da kuma wuyansa.
'Yan sandan jihar Louisiana sun ce, rundunar' yan sandan jihar Louisiana, da 'yan sandan jihar, da 'yan sandan jami'ar Southern University da kuma mazauna yankin sun taimaka a binciken da ya kai ga kama mutumin.
Daraktan wasannin motsa jiki na LSU Joe Alleva ya gode wa 'yan sanda da ke yankin saboda "hankali da kuma bin doka da oda".
Sims yana da shekara 20.
Dan wasan tsayi ne mai tsawon kafa 6 da inci da rabi, ya taso ne a Baton Rouge, inda mahaifinsa, Wayne, ya buga wasan kwando a kungiyar LSU.
Ya ci gaba da samun maki 5.6 da kuma rebounds 2.6 a wasan karshe.
A safiyar yau Juma'a, kocin 'yan wasan LSU, Will Wade ya ce, "Jami'ar ta yi matukar bakin ciki da kuma girgiza kan mutuwar Wade".
"Wannan shi ne abin da kuke tsoron", in ji Wade.
Dutsen da ke ƙonewa yana ta da ƙura a kan birnin Mexico
Ash da aka zubo daga dutsen da ake kira Popocatepetl ya kai kudancin babban birnin Mexico.
A ranar Asabar ne cibiyar hana bala'i ta kasa ta gargadi jama'ar Mexico da su guji zuwa wurin da dutsen ya yi dajin, bayan da aka samu tashin hankali a cikin dutsen da aka yi a cikin sa'o'i 24 da aka samu gurbatacciyar iska da kuma turɓaya guda 183.
Cibiyar ta lura da rawar da ake yi a cikin gidajen da ke cikin gidaje da kuma girgizar ƙasa a wurare da yawa.
Hotuna a shafukan sada zumunta sun nuna yadudduka na toka a kan tagogin mota a unguwannin Mexico City kamar Xochimilco.
Masana ilimin kasa da kasa sun lura da karuwar ayyukan a cikin dutsen mai fitad da wuta, mai nisan kilomita 72 kudu maso gabashin babban birnin kasar, tun lokacin da girgizar kasa mai girman 7.1 ta girgiza tsakiyar Mexico a watan Satumbar 2017.
Dutsen mai aman wuta da ake kira "Don Goyo" ya kasance yana aiki tun shekara ta 1994.
'Yan sanda sun yi arangama da masu neman 'yancin kai na Catalonia kafin bikin ranar zaɓewa
An kama mutane shida a Barcelona a ranar Asabar bayan masu zanga-zangar neman 'yancin kai sun yi karo da jami'an tsaro yayin da dubban mutane suka shiga zanga-zangar nuna adawa da juna da ke nuna ranar tunawa da zabubbukan da aka kada a kan 'yancin kai a Catalonia.
Wasu 'yan tawaye da ke sanye da makamai sun tsare 'yan sanda, sun yi ta jefa fure-fure da kuma turare a kan titunan da ke cike da masu yawon bude ido.
An kuma samu fada a cikin dare inda 'yan sanda suka yi amfani da sanduna don su yi yaƙi.
A cikin sa'o'i da yawa, kungiyoyin 'yancin kai suna ta ihu "Babu abin da aka manta, babu abin da aka gafarta", kuma an tarar da masu zanga-zangar Unionist suna ta ihu "Long live Spain".
'Yan jarida na yankin sun ruwaito cewa mutane 14 sun samu rauni a lokacin zanga-zangar.
Zaben ya ci gaba da kasancewa cikin tashin hankali a yankin da ke neman 'yancin kai shekara guda bayan kada kuri'ar 1 ga Oktoba, wanda aka ayyana a matsayin ba bisa ka'ida ba daga Madrid, amma 'yan Catalan masu ra'ayin' yanci sun yi bikin.
Masu jefa kuri'a sun yi murmushi a kan neman 'yancin kai, amma masu adawa da 'yancin kai sun yi kasa da kasa, kuma wadanda suka yi adawa da 'yancin kai sun yi kauracewa a kuri'ar.
A cewar hukumomin Catalonia, kusan mutane 1,000 ne suka samu raunuka a bara bayan da 'yan sanda suka yi kokarin hana zaben a lokacin da ake ta gwagwarmaya a wuraren zabe a fadin yankin.
Kungiyoyin 'yanci sun yi zango a daren ranar Juma'a don hana wani gangami da 'yan sanda suka yi.
An yi zanga-zangar amma an tilasta wa 'yan ta'adda su bi wata hanya dabam.
Narcis Termes, mai shekara 68, wani mai aikin lantarki wanda ya halarci zanga-zangar 'yancin kai tare da matarsa, ya ce ba ya jin tsoron fatan cewa Catalonia za ta samu 'yancin kai.
"Shekarar da ta gabata, mun yi wata rana mafi farin ciki.
Na ga iyayena suna kuka da farin ciki saboda an ba su damar yin zabe, amma yanzu mun makale", in ji shi.
Duk da cewa sun samu nasara a zaben yankin da aka yi a watan Disambar da ya gabata, jam'iyyun neman 'yancin Catalonia sun yi ta fama da ci gaba da samun ci gaba, kuma da yawa daga cikin sanannun shugabanninsu sun yi gudun hijira ko kuma a tsare suke, suna jiran a hukunta su saboda rawar da suka taka wajen gudanar da zaben da kuma sanar da 'yancin kai.
Joan Puig, mai aikin injiniya, mai shekara 42, ya yi rikodin zanga-zangar a kan wayarsa a matsayin goyon baya ga 'yan sanda, yana mai cewa, 'yan siyasa ne suka haifar da rikicin a bangarorin biyu.
"Tashin hankali yana ƙaruwa", in ji shi.
A ranar Asabar Oriol Junqueras, daya daga cikin shugabannin Catalonia tara da ke jiran a yi musu shari'a tun a bara, ya ce zai tsaya takara a zaben zaben 'yan majalisar Turai na shekara mai zuwa.
"Samun takara a zaben Turai shi ne hanya mafi kyau na kaucewa koma bayan dabi'un dimokiradiyya da kuma cin mutuncin da muka gani daga gwamnatin Spain", in ji shi.
