A wasan da ya buga da Rovers, Livingston ya yi nasara a kan Rangers, inda ya ci Steven Gerrard a karo na biyu a kwallaye 18 da ya yi a kungiyar Ibrox.
Dolly Menga ta jefa kwallo mai ban mamaki a wasan da ya kawo sauyi, inda tawagar Gary Holt ta koma gefe da Hibernian a matsayi na biyu.
A gasar bana, tawagar Gerrard ba ta yi nasara a gasar ba, kuma za ta fafata da Hearts, wadda take da maki takwas a ragar da ta yi a ranar Lahadi mai zuwa.
Kafin wannan lokacin, Ranger za su yi wa Rapid Vienna ziyara a gasar Europa a ranar Alhamis.
A gefe guda kuma, Livingston yana ƙara wa ƙungiyarsa nasara a wasanni shida, kuma koci Holt bai taɓa shan kashi ba tun da ya maye gurbin Kenny Miller a watan da ya gabata.
Livingston ya yi hasarar chances a kan tsabar kudi rashin
A'a, ƙungiyar Holt ya kamata ta riga ta kai gaci kafin ta ci kwallaye, kuma yadda suka taka leda da sauri ya jawo wa Rangers matsala sosai.
Scott Robinson ya tsallake, amma ya ci kwallo a gaban raga, sai Alan Lithgow ya ci kwallo a waje da raga, bayan ya yi tsalle ya ci kwallo a kan raga, ya buga kwallo a gaban raga.
Ƙungiyar da ke gida sun gamsu da barin Rangers su yi wasa a gaban su, domin sun san cewa za su iya jawo wa ƙungiyar matsala idan suka yi wasa a ƙwallon ƙafa.
Kuma a cikin wannan yanayi ne babban burinmu ya zo.
Yan wasan Rangers sun ci kwallo, Livingston ya ci kwallo, Declan Gallagher da Robinson sun hada kwallo, wanda ya yi taɓawa kuma ya ci daga tsakiyar filin.
A lokacin, Rangers sun mamaye mallakar kwallon, amma suna gwagwarmaya don shiga cikin tsaron gida, kuma mai tsaron gida Liam Kelly ba shi da ƙalubalen ƙalubale.
Wannan yanayin ya ci gaba har zuwa rabi na biyu, ko da yake Alfredo Morelos ya ci nasara a kan Kelly.
Scott Pittman ya harbe shi da ƙafafunsa daga mai tsaron gidan Rangers Allan McGregor, kuma Lithgow ya harbe shi a waje a wani yanayi na mutuwar Livingston.
Aikin da aka ci gaba da shiga filin Livingston, amma an ƙi shi, kuma an ƙi buƙatun biyu don bugun penalty  bayan bugun Halkett a kan mai maye gurbin Glenn Middleton da kuma hannu ɗaya a kan ƙwallon.
