Yan wasan kungiyar da kuma kungiyarsu ba su canza ba tun bayan komawarsu zuwa gasar zakarun Turai, amma babban bangare na yabo ya kamata ya tafi ga Holt saboda yadda ya kara karfafa kungiyar tun lokacin da ya shiga.
Akwai jarumawa da yawa.
Shugaban 'yan wasan, Halkett, ya kasance mai ban mamaki kuma ya jagoranci tsaro mai kyau, kuma Menga ya riƙe Connor Goldson da Joe Worrall a kan kafafu a cikin dukan wasan.
Amma Ranger ya yi rashin wahayi.
A wasu lokatai, sun yi wasa sosai a ƙarƙashin Gerrard, amma ba su yi wasa mai kyau ba.
Ƙarshen wasan da suka yi bai da kyau sosai, sau ɗaya kawai suka ci nasara a kan 'yan wasan gida, kuma hakan ya sa 'yan wasan Rangers suka yi rawar gani, domin sun fi kowa yin nasara a wasan da suka yi.
