LeBron zai fara buga wa Lakers wasa a San Diego ranar Lahadi
Jiran da ake yi na ganin LeBron James ya buga wasan farko na Lakers ya kusa karewa.
Kocin Lakers, Luke Walton ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan farko na kakar wasa ta bana da za a yi ranar Lahadi da kuma Denver Nuggets a San Diego.
Amma ba a ƙayyade yawan lokacin da zai yi wasa ba.
"Zai zama fiye da 1 kuma kasa da 48", in ji Walton a shafin Lakers.
Mai watsa labaran Lakers Mike Trudell ya wallafa a shafinsa na Twitter cewa James mai yiwuwa ba zai buga duka wasan ba.
Bayan an kammala wasan a farkon makon nan, an tambayi James game da shirinsa na buga wasanni shida da Lakers za su yi kafin a fara kakar wasa ta bana.
"A matsayina na mai tsere, ba na bukatar yin wasa kafin lokaci don in samu nutsuwa", in ji shi.
Taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara wani gangami na masu zaɓe a Wheeling, West Virginia a daren yau.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko cikin jerin tarurrukan da Trump zai yi a makon gobe, ciki har da tarurruka a wurare masu goyon bayan Trump kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da aka dakatar da zaben tabbatar da za a zabi wanda Trump ya zaba a matsayin alkalin da zai hau kotun koli, Trump na kokarin samun goyon baya a zaben da za a yi a tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar hadarin rasa ikon su a majalisar dokoki a lokacin da za a kada kuri'ar a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za a yi zaben shugaban kasa na shekara ta 2020 a West Virginia, kuma yaya kake kallon shi a yanar gizo?
Za a gudanar da taron zaɓe na Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia a tsakar dare (lokacin Denmark) tsakanin Asabar, 29 ga Nuwamba da Lahadi, 30 ga Nuwamba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon zaben Trump a West Virginia ta hanyar yanar gizo ta hanyar watsa shirye-shirye a YouTube.
A yayin da ake sa ran za a yi zaben tabbatar da kujerar shugabancin Amurka, Trump zai yi jawabi a kan shari'ar da ake yi a wannan makon, a kan wanda aka zaɓa a matsayin babban alkali, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya fuskanci kalubale a kan zargin aikata laifukan jima'i, kuma ana sa ran za a yi wani taro a majalisar dattijai don tabbatar da kujerar shugabancin, amma an dakatar da shi har tsawon mako guda, yayin da hukumar FBI ke ci gaba da binciken tuhumar da ake yi wa shi.
Amma babban burin wannan zagaye na zaben shi ne samar da wani sabon salo ga 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar wani zabe mai wuya a watan Nuwamba.
Jami'an yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump sun ce za a gudanar da zagaye biyar na zaɓe a mako mai zuwa don "samar da kuzari a tsakanin 'yan sa kai da magoya baya yayin da 'yan Republican ke ƙoƙarin karewa da kuma ƙara yawanci da suke da shi a Majalisar Dattawa da kuma Majalisar Wakilai", a cewar Reuters.
"Gwamnatin da ke kan majalisar dokoki tana da muhimmanci ga ajandar shugaban, har shugaban zai ziyarci jihohi da yawa kamar yadda zai yiwu, yayin da muke shiga cikin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani mai magana da yawun Trump, wanda bai so a ambaci sunansa ba, ya ce wa Reuters.
Taron na wannan yammacin da za a yi a filin wasa na Wesbanco Arena da ke Wheeling, ana sa ran zai jawo hankalin magoya bayan Trump daga "Ohio da Pennsylvania, kuma za a samu rahoto daga Pittsburgh", in ji West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar, za a sake yin wani ziyara na biyu a watan nan da Trump ya ziyarci jihar West Virginia, jihar da ya yi nasara da kashi 40 cikin 100 a shekarar 2016.
A wannan karon, Trump na kokarin taimakawa dan takarar da ke neman takara a majalisar dattawa ta West Virginia, Patrick Morrisey, wanda ke bin sahun baya a zaben fidda gwani.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrisey cewa shugaban ya bukaci ya yi amfani da shi don ya ba shi kwarin gwiwa a cikin ƙididdigar", in ji Simon Haeder, wanda ke nazarin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters.
