A ranar Lahadi, kungiyar Ibrox ta yi nasarar lashe kofin farko a filin daga tun bayan da suka yi nasara a St Johnstone da ci 4-1 a watan Fabrairu, amma tawagar Gary Holt ta ci Gerrard ne a karo na biyu a wasa 18 da ya buga a matsayin koci, inda ya sa suka yi nasara da maki takwas.
Menga ya buga a minti bakwai kafin a dakatar da shi, wanda ba a ba da izini ba, Ranger ba zai iya amsawa ba.
Rangers sun sauka zuwa matsayi na shida, yayin da Livingston ya hau zuwa matsayi na uku bayan Hibernian da kawai ya bambanta da raga.
Kuma akwai wasu labarai marasa dadi a kan hanya ga 'yan Rangers, yayin da alkalin wasa Calum Spence ya bukaci kulawa bayan da aka harbe shi a kan kai da wani abu da ya fito daga bangaren da ake kira "Rainbow".
Gerrard ya yi canje-canje takwas a cikin rukunin da ya kai wasan kusa da na karshe na gasar cin kofin Betfed, inda ya wuce Ayr.
Holt, a gefe guda, yana wasa da 'yan wasa 11 da suka rage maki daya daga kan Hearts a makon da ya gabata, kuma zai yi farin cikin ganin yadda 'yan wasa masu basira suka yi nasara a ko'ina.
Ranger ya fi kowa yin nasara, amma Livingston ya fi shi yin nasara.
Ya kamata su ci kwallaye biyu a cikin minti na farko na wasan, lokacin da wasan farko na Menga ya sa Scott Pittman ya ci gaba da Allan McGregor, amma dan wasan tsakiya ya yi ƙoƙari ya wuce.
A cikin rami, wani mai tsaron gida daga Keaghan Jacobs ya sami hanyar kai wa Kyaftin Craig Halkett, amma mai tsaron baya Alan Lithgow ya ci gaba da buga kwallo a kan na baya.
Ko da yake 'yan Rangers sun ci nasara, sun dogara ne da bege maimakon iyawa a wasan da suka buga.
Ba a san ko wane ne ya yi nasara ba, sai dai Alfredo Morales ya yi farin ciki da alƙali Steven Thomson ya ƙi amincewa da ƙarar da 'yan Colombian suka yi na neman a ba su bugun daga ƙofar bayan ya yi wasa da Steven Lawless bayan ya yi wasa da ƙwallon ƙafa.
A cikin wasan farko, Ranger sun zura kwallaye biyu ne kawai a raga, amma tsohon mai tsaron gida Liam Kelly bai damu da bugun da Lassana Coulibaly ya yi ba da kuma bugun da Ovie Ejaria ya yi ba.
Ko da yake Livis ya buɗe wasan a minti na 34 ne kawai, amma ya cancanci a ce ya yi hakan ne don ƙoƙarce-ƙoƙarcen da suka yi.
A karo na biyu, Ranger ba zai iya jimre wa matsalar da Jacobs ya kawo ba.
Scott Arfield bai yi wani abu ba, lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya ba Scott Robinson, wanda ya dauki lokaci don neman Menga, wanda zai iya jefa shi a raga.
A lokacin da aka shiga cikin wasan, Gerrard ya maye gurbin Coulibaly da Ryan Kent, wanda ya yi nasara kusan nan take, lokacin da mai kunnawa ya ba da kwallon zuwa Morelos, amma Kelly mai kyau ya gudu daga matsayinsa don toshewa.
Amma, sai Livingston ya sa ƙungiyarsa ta buga ƙwallo mai yawa a filin wasa na Lithgow da Halkett.
Holt ya iya karawa da farko a wasan, amma McGregor ya yi watsi da Jacobs da hannu kafin Lithgow ya kai kusa da burin.
Mai wasan Rangers Glenn Middleton ya sake yin kira don jinkirta bugun daga daga bugun daga baya bayan ya yi wasa tare da Jacobs, amma alƙali Thomson ya sake duba wannan.
Littafin shekara: Wanda Ya Yi Na'urar Ƙidayar Geiger
Kuma yanzu shafi daga littafin shekara na "Sunday Morning": Satumba 30, 1882, shekaru 136 da suka wuce a yau - idan muka ƘIDADI... - ranar da aka haifi masanin kimiyyar nan gaba Johannes Wilhelm "Hans" Geiger a Jamus.
Geiger ya ƙirƙiri wata hanya ta gano da kuma auna rediyo, ƙirar da za ta kai ga na'urar da aka sani da Geiger Counter.
Ƙididdigar Geiger ta zama muhimmiyar al'ada a cikin kimiyya da kuma al'adun gargajiya, kamar yadda aka nuna a cikin fim ɗin "Bells of Coronado" na shekara ta 1950, wanda Roy Rogers da Dale Evans suka yi fim ɗin suna "Bells of Coronado" a matsayin 'yan kimiyya na ƙauye:
Mutumin: "Mene ne wannan?"
Rogers: "Wannan na'urar ƙidayar Geiger ce, wadda ake amfani da ita wajen neman ma'adanai masu ɗaukan rediyo kamar su uranium.
"Idan ka saka waɗannan belun kunne, za ka iya jin tasirin da ake samu a jikin atoms, wato yadda ake yin rediyo a cikin ma'adanai".
Evans: "Ku yi haƙuri, muna da wannan!"
"Hans" Geiger ya mutu a shekara ta 1945 kwanaki kaɗan kafin ya cika shekara 63.
