Bayan wani jawabi da ya yi a wani shiri na Saturday Night Live, Kanye West ya yi fushi sosai lokacin da ya yaba wa shugaban Amurka Donald Trump, kuma ya ce zai yi takarar shugaban kasa a 2020.
Bayan ya buga waƙar ta uku a daren, wato "Ghost Town" da ke ɗauke da ƙyallen "Make America Great Again", sai ya soma yin waƙar ƙyallen "Democrat" kuma ya ci gaba da goyon bayan Trump.
"Ina yawan magana da mutanen da suke da fata da fata, suna cewa, 'Me ya sa kuke son Trump, shi ɗan wari ne?'
