A shirinsa na farko, SNL ya nuna wani wasan kwaikwayo na Matt Damon, inda tauraron Hollywood ya yi ba'a game da shaidar da Brett Kavanaugh ya bayar a gaban kwamitin shari'a na Majalisar Dattijai game da tuhumar Christine Blasey Ford da ake yi wa fyade.
Ko da yake ba a nuna bidiyon ba, dan wasan wasan kwaikwayo Chris Rock West ya wallafa rainin hankali a kan kafofin watsa labarun.
