Dan wasan Tennessee State Tigers Christion Abercrombie ya samu gaggawar tiyata bayan da ya ji rauni a kai a wasan da suka yi a ranar Asabar 31 ga watan 27 ga watan 31 ga watan 31 ga watan 27 ga watan 31 a wasan da suka yi da Vanderbilt Commodores, kamar yadda majiyar 'yan jarida ta Tennessee Mike Organ ta ruwaito.
Kocin Tennessee State, Rod Reed, ya gaya wa manema labarai cewa, abin ya faru ne kafin hutun wasan.
"Ya fita zuwa gefen kuma ya fadi a can", in ji Reed.
Masu koyarwa da likitoci sun ba Abercrombie iskar oxygen a gefen hanya kafin su saka shi a kan wani akwati kuma su kai shi don ƙarin bincike.
Wani mai magana da yawun jihar Tennessee ya shaida wa Chris Harris na WSMV a Nashville, Tennessee cewa an dakatar da aikin Abercrombie a cibiyar likitocin Vanderbilt.
Harris ya kara da cewa, "babu wani bayani game da irin ko kuma yawan lalacewar har yanzu", kuma jihar Tennessee tana kokarin gano lokacin da ya zargi kansa da lalacewar.
Abercrombie yana cikin shekararsa ta biyu a Tennessee State, kuma yana buga wa'adinsa na farko a Tennessee State bayan da ya yi canji daga Illinois.
