2004: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi da ta auku a gabar tekun yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra ya haifar da tsunami a ranar 26 ga Disamba, wanda ya shafi ƙasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, ciki har da fiye da rabin waɗanda ke Aceh.
2005: An yi girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfi a yammacin gabar tekun Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
