Ana ta yin ihu a yakin cinikayya tsakanin Amurka da China, kuma duk da cewa har yanzu ba a kammala ba, to amma a dogon lokaci, takwarorinsu sun ce, rashin jituwa tsakanin kasashen biyu zai iya amfani Beijing.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump ya yi gargadi a farkon wannan shekarar ta hanyar sanya haraji kan kayayyakin da kasar Sin ke fitarwa, kamar bangarorin hasken rana, da karafa da kuma aluminum.
Babban tashin hankali a wannan makon na sabbin haraji, wanda ya shafi kayayyaki da suka kai dala biliyan 200, ya shafi kusan rabin dukkan kayayyakin da ake shigowa da su Amurka daga China.
A kowane lokaci Beijing ta yi martani, a kwanan nan ta sanya haraji na 5-10% kan kayayyakin Amurka na dala biliyan 60.
