Syria 'a shirye take' ta karbi 'yan gudun hijira, in ji Ministan Harkokin Wajen Kasar
Syria ta ce a shirye take ta karɓi 'yan gudun hijirar da za su koma gida, kuma ta nemi taimako don sake gina ƙasar da ta lalace sakamakon yaƙin da aka yi na tsawon shekara bakwai.
Ministan harkokin waje na kasar, Walid al-Moualem, a jawabinsa ga Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, ya ce al'amura suna kara gyaruwa a kasar.
"A yau, halin da ake ciki ya fi karko da tsaro saboda nasarar da aka samu a yaki da ta'addanci", in ji shi.
Gwamnati na ci gaba da kula da yankunan da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata, kuma tana kokarin dawo da al'ada.
Yanzu an sami damar da za a mayar da 'yan gudun hijirar zuwa ƙasar da suka bar saboda 'yan ta'adda da kuma takunkumin tattalin arziki da aka yi wa al'ummarsu da kuma rayuwarsu.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa sama da 'yan Siriya miliyan 5.5 ne suka tsere daga kasar tun daga shekarar 2011, lokacin da yaki ya barke.
Sauran mutane miliyan shida da ke cikin ƙasar na bukatar taimakon gaggawa.
Al-Moualem ya ce gwamnatin Siriya za ta yi farin cikin karbar taimako don sake gina kasar da aka lalata.
Amma ya jaddada cewa gwamnati ba za ta amince da taimako ko kuma tallafi daga kasashe da ke tallafawa tawayen ba.
Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Paris
Tawagar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup 2018 kuma ta doke ta Amurka da 16.5 - 10.5 a Le Golf National a waje da Paris.
Amurka ta sha kashi shida a jere a Turai kuma ba ta taba lashe kofin Ryder ba a Turai tun 1993.
Ƙasar Turai ta sake samun nasarar cin kofin a lokacin da tawagar Thomas Bjørn ta kai maki 14.5 da ake bukata don a doke Amirka.
Dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya sha wahala a yawancin wasan, ya harbi kwallo a par 3 a rami na 16, wanda ya sa ya rasa wasan da Francesco Molinari.
Molinari na Italiya ya yi kyau a kowane zagaye kuma ya zama 1 daga cikin 'yan wasa 4 da suka sami 5-0-0 tun 1979, lokacin da aka fara gasar ta yanzu.
Ba'amurke Jordan Spieth ya fice da 5&4 daga hannun dan wasan Turai mafi karancin daraja, Danish Thorbjørn Olesen.
Dan wasan da ya fi kowanne a duniya, Dustin Johnson, ya fadi biyu da daya a hannun Ian Poulter na Ingila, wanda a yanzu haka, zai iya zama ya yi wasan Ryder Cup na karshe.
Tsohon ɗan wasan da ya lashe gasar Ryder Cup takwas, ɗan ƙasar Spain Sergio Garcia, ya zama ɗan Turai da ya fi kowa cin nasara a gasar, ya ci kwallo 25.5.
"Ba na yawan yin kuka, amma yau ba na jin daɗin yin hakan.
Shekara ta kasance mai wuya.
Na yi farin ciki cewa Thomas ya zaɓe ni kuma ya gaskata da ni.
Ina farin ciki da na samu wannan kyautar.
Wannan aikin kungiya ne kuma ina farin cikin taimaka", in ji Garcia bayan nasarar da ya yi a Turai.
Ya ba da wannan hasken ga ɗan ƙasarsa John Ram, wanda ya doke Tiger Woods, ɗan wasan golf na Amirka, sau biyu da kuma sau ɗaya a wasan da ya yi a ranar Lahadi.
Rahm, mai shekara 23, ya ce: "Ina alfahari da na doke Tiger Woods, na bi shi tun ina yaro".
Woods ya sha kashi a duka wasanni huɗu da ya buga a Faransa kuma yanzu ya ci nasara a gasar Ryder Cup da ci 13-21-3.
Wannan lamari ne mai ban mamaki ga daya daga cikin manyan 'yan wasan golf a tarihi, wanda ya lashe manyan kyaututtuka 14, wanda Jack Nicklaus ne ya fi nasara.
Kungiyar Amurkawa sun sha wahala a duk karshen mako, sai dai Patrick Reed, Justin Thomas da Tony Finau sun yi rawar gani a duk fafatawar da suka yi.
Bayan wasan da 'yan wasan suka yi, sai shugaban 'yan wasan Amirka Jim Furyk ya ce: "Ina alfahari da 'yan wasan, domin sun yi yaƙi don gaskiya.
Akwai sauran lokaci a wannan safiya da muka ba wa Turai damar yin nasara.
Mun yi rashin nasara.
Ina mika sakon girmamawa ga Thomas.
Shi kyaftin ne mai kyau.
Dukan 'yan wasansa 12 suna wasa sosai.
Za mu sake tsara ƙungiyoyi kuma zan yi aiki tare da PGA na Amurka da kuma kwamitin Ryder Cup ɗinmu, sannan mu ci gaba.
Ina son 'yan'uwa 12 da suke wa'azi a ƙasar waje, kuma ina alfaharin zama kyaftininsu.
Dole ne ku sauƙaƙe hat.
An ci mu da yaƙi".
